headline: Trump Is Rallying Bank Stocks Like Truist and Citizens. Why They Can Keep Gaining.
summary: Bank stocks have had a solid January, and regional-bank stocks, and the ETF, look set to rise for the rest of the year.

headline: Truist to speak at the UBS Financial Services Conference
summary: Truist Financial Corporation (NYSE: TFC) today announced that Chief Financial Officer Mike Maguire will speak at the UBS Financial Services Conference on Tuesday, Feb. 11, 2025, at 1:00 p.m. ET.
